text.tspan: We have at ESRF a large number of motor
ex : piezo, high precision, high load motors
Our objective was then to propose a framework to :
*Ease the usage of motors in modern control system:
Mathias Guijaro, Cyril Guilloud, Manuel Perez - BLISS unit - ESRF
We are presenting here a generic python framework for motors control. It allows to easily and
rapidly interface motor controllers offering common features to a control system.
Thanks to all the Beamline Control unit
for their always kind advices and suggestions
E-Motion framework is already in use on some ESRF beamlines.
- It drives the sample stage on nano-imaging ID16a
beamline ~1 nm repeatability achieved with a piezo hexapod
- It is used for new spectrometer tests on ID26
Key paradigms : Configuration ; Axis; Groups; Controller plugins.
